Package udel.GardenProject.garden

All the critical code that brings the application together and runs it.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Team 0
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Contains the start and real main, setups different components of the application.
    Main
    Main entry point for the GardenProject application to bypass JavaFX errors.
    Model
    Updates the stage: Contains logic and data.
    Session
    Holds all the critical user-state information so that a .gardenproject file can be easily loaded in and out without much delay.

    Isolated so that it can be saved and loaded easily.

    All attributes should be adequately javadoc'd for future reference.

    NOTE: All attributes should be initialized to a default value, either in their attribute or the Session constructor.
    View
    Creates the stage: Loads graphics, images, and defines what the user sees.
